<h2 id="main-riff">Main riff</h2>

<p>The main riff uses the notes below. I use my middle finger for the 7-6-5-3 fretted notes on the low E string. The hard part will be transitioning into the E-major chord while maintaining your rhythm in a strumâ€¦ and likewise transitioning from that same strummy E-major back into this riff.</p>

